{"PageNumber":20,"Angle":0,"RotatedAngle":0,"Height":817,"Width":1089,"OriginHeight":0,"OriginWidth":0,"Elements":[{"Index":0,"Type":"title","Text":"#  Advantages of Iterative Waterfall Model","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":27,"Y":64},"LeftTop":{"X":27,"Y":23},"RightBottom":{"X":667,"Y":64},"RightTop":{"X":667,"Y":23}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":1,"Type":"table","Text":"<table><tr><td>Feedback Path</td></tr><tr><td>In the classical waterfall model, there are no feedback paths, so there is no mechanism for error correction. But in the iterative waterfall model feedback path from one phase to its preceding phase allows correcting the errors that are committed and these changes are reflected in the later phases.</td></tr></table>","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":84,"Y":349},"LeftTop":{"X":84,"Y":94},"RightBottom":{"X":1006,"Y":349},"RightTop":{"X":1006,"Y":94}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":2,"Type":"table","Text":"<table><tr><td>Simple</td></tr><tr><td>Very simple to understand and use.</td></tr></table>","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":84,"Y":459},"LeftTop":{"X":84,"Y":368},"RightBottom":{"X":1006,"Y":459},"RightTop":{"X":1006,"Y":368}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":3,"Type":"table","Text":"<table><tr><td>Separation of Phases</td></tr><tr><td>The clear separation of phases allows for better planning and management of the project, as each phase has specific goals and deliverables.</td></tr></table>","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":84,"Y":652},"LeftTop":{"X":84,"Y":481},"RightBottom":{"X":1006,"Y":652},"RightTop":{"X":1006,"Y":481}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":4,"Type":"table","Text":"<table><tr><td>Well-organized</td></tr><tr><td>Less time is consumed on documenting and the team can spend more time on development and designing.</td></tr></table>","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":84,"Y":800},"LeftTop":{"X":84,"Y":667},"RightBottom":{"X":1006,"Y":800},"RightTop":{"X":1006,"Y":667}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":5,"Type":"footer","Text":"13","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":1045,"Y":787},"LeftTop":{"X":1045,"Y":766},"RightBottom":{"X":1066,"Y":787},"RightTop":{"X":1066,"Y":766}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""}]}